        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yes, and I was wondering if you had any ideas."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Now that I think about it, a while ago, I heard about a device related to souls from a certain alchemist."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Really!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yes. And there is a certain item that's absolutely necessary for the creation of such a device."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Let's see, they actually told me the recipe. Give me a minute..."
